g primary BHs. Therefore, the formation scenario of\nthese atypical BH-BH mergers remains to be found.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 17:59:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 15:16:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
