ures without the need to go through the time-consuming physical\nimplementation flow. The machine learning algorithms show great potentials as a\nmeans for evaluation and optimization of new CMOS technologies and identifying\nthe most significant technology design parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Sep 2021 04:39:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-17"}
